title: One To Remember | Carlsen vs Caruana | Bilbao Masters (2012)
description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Magnus Carlsen vs Fabiano Caruana
Bilbao Masters Tiebreak (2012) (blitz), Bilbao ESP, rd 2, Oct-13 
Formation: King's Indian Attack (A07)

1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. g3 b6 4. Bg2 Bb7 5. Qe2 d6 6. d4 cd4 7. Nd4 Nf6 8. O-O Nbd7 9. Rd1 a6 10. e5 Bg2 11. ef6 Bh3 12. Qh5 Qf6 13. Qh3 Be7 14. Nc3 Qg6 15. Nc6 Ne5 16. Ne7 Ke7 17. Bf4

Photos from http://www.chessdom.com/magnus-carlsen-wins-txapela-in-the-5th-final-masters/
